<div class="support-page header-margin-top">
  <h2>Support</h2>
  <div class="support-wrapper">
    <section class="support-section">
      <h3>Download Website PDF</h3>
      <p>
        If you experience issues while generating PDF files, please contact support at <a href="mailto:support@boringsoft.io">support@boringsoft.io</a>.
      </p>
      <div class="support-actions">
        <a class="support-button" href="mailto:support@boringsoft.io?subject=Download%20Website%20PDF%20Support">
          Contact Support
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="support-section">
      <h3>Before reporting an issue</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Make sure you are using the latest version of the extension.</li>
        <li>Refresh the webpage and try again.</li>
        <li>Check whether the issue occurs on multiple websites.</li>
        <li>Try restarting Chrome.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <section class="support-section">
      <h3>Useful information to include</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Website URL where the issue occurred.</li>
        <li>Chrome version.</li>
        <li>Extension version.</li>
        <li>Description of the problem.</li>
        <li>Screenshot or screen recording if available.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <section class="support-section">
      <h3>Privacy</h3>
      <p>
        Download Website PDF generates PDF files locally in your browser. Webpage content is not uploaded to our servers.
      </p>
      <p>
        Read the full
        <a href="/privacy-policy/">Privacy Policy</a>.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</div>